    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some visible clear coat peeling and a few minor dings, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the suspension is starting to feel loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable entry into this model who doesn't mind performing some light restorative work.",
