      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an accessible price point. While the car is mechanically sound and starts reliably, the exterior shows some visible wear including minor scratches and faded paint in a few spots. The interior is intact but shows typical signs of use like slight seat wear and some aged plastic trim. It has been maintained enough to stay on the road, but a new owner should expect to address some minor cosmetic issues and routine maintenance items in the near future.",
